==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Atomize
<hw>At"om*ize</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To reduce to atoms, or to fine
spray.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The liquids in the form of spray are said to be pulverized,
nebulized, or <qex>atomized</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Dunglison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

